nd: white; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">第六部分：回归泥土，回归家庭，以生命供养生命</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 3px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; background: white; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">第</span><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">16</span><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">讲：我们都有童年，小时候与泥土为伴。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 3px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; background: white; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">第</span><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">17</span><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">讲：“教育</span><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">+</span><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">文化</span><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">+</span><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">旅游”，最好的教育方式。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 3px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; background: white; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">第</span><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding