rtant;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这门课程将涉及<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">国家宏观政策认知与解读、一带一路、雄安新区、长江经济带、振兴乡村、更新城市、文旅IP打造与构建、中国式自信、文旅产业服务、养生大健康产业、自然教育、研学旅行、全域旅游、厕所革命、供给侧改革、互联网+、生态文明</strong>等，我将通过一个全新的视角进行通盘诠释，这是一门<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">华夏文化溯源、中国式自信回归、打破三观与重建</strong>的课程，让我们一同领略未来波澜壮阔的文旅中国。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appf3KZT3728192/image/ueditor/13000_1541637247.cn/mmbiz_jpg/b4mklbpgc03hfxrrqfnmuinoanzhxmciamica7rupe6y8dmzqqiauhdsq6tibky5de4qbo3oczmickkkrvgu5giattlg/640" style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">1、文旅产业是未来三十年的风口产业。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">文旅产业是未来最大的第三产业，并可能由此衍生进化出第四产业，第五产业</strong>；一切文化旅游<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">服务和消费互联网化、数字化、智能化、产业服务年轻化。</strong>互联网像火、数据像新大陆、计算像电力：在线，未来的一切都在线。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">2、一切都是数据都是信用都是服务；流动，未来一切都是一摊流动的数据、流动的服务，文化旅游服务消费的动态性更强进；<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">计算和万物互联，文化旅游产业的大数据系统已经在悄然成行，我们又被重新定义在新的服务体系和系统里；</strong>产业服务的年轻化，80，90后成为产业服务主流群体，尤其科技服务与创新，获客成本大大降低。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">3、未来文旅、未来一切都离不开研习、经营，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">世界风云变化唯有掌握本质、不离其宗；</strong>大可营国，中可营城，小可营小镇、村庄、综合体、产业园、庄园、民宿；可不是走马观花，研习好文旅这门课程，可以立身、治家、兴业。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">这与修身齐家治国平天下的中国天道文明观是高度一致的。</strong>文旅研习的这门学问我称之为文旅道治学，文旅研习的根本目的是经营，经天纬地，学以致用。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">4、那么文旅的真正定义是什么呢？<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">以天文定人文，以人文施行教化，这就是文化。以天文定地理，人的肉体驱动地理位移变化，这就是旅游，</strong>也就是传统位移旅游。文化和旅游的人文交媾这就是文化旅游，简称文旅。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">5、观天象，授农时，指导农耕，这就是农耕文明，天文历法的根本是指导农业生产，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">历史上我们修正天文历法的目的也是为了更好的更准确的指导农业生产。</strong>这是农耕文明的根本，应了天时地利人和，什么时候，什么山开什么花，什么地方结什么果。这是我们的文化本源。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">6、文旅真正的根本和基础其实就是我们在表现形式上看到的一年四季、十二月、二十四节气，以二十四节气，以自然为根本，以农耕为根本的这些根本，也就是说文旅要反刍到我们农耕文明的这个体系里面来，这是她真正的基础，真正的出发点。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">7、但在互联网化、数字化、智能化、产业服务年轻化，技术崇拜、数据主义会把我们给变懒、智力下降、甚至人文消亡。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">我们的进化逐渐从灵性生命到人文生命到工业生命再到数据生命。</strong>我们离自然界越来越远，人文生命离消亡就越近，所以靠近自然回归自然会成为一种天然需求。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">8、想越来越不被社会淘汰，我们选择正向化的演进；想越来越不被消亡，针对大生命周期的消亡我们选择逆向化进化，回归自然成为必然选择。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">回归自然就是旅游，就是回归到我们种族记忆里那个家，回归到母体，与自然为一的家。</strong>我们在技术演进和自然回归这两种选择之间，进行着随时的抉择和切换。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">9、实际上旅游的形式应该分为多种，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">书本，冲浪，影像，智能vr、ar虚拟现实，现实出游，梦境。</strong>对于人来说，神游是最高形式。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">10、<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">物流，人流，资金流，信息流，</strong>这是最基本的游动形式，也是泛指的旅游。物流是物质的旅游，资金流是金钱的旅游，信息流是信息的旅游，人流是人的旅游，我们指的旅游通常是以人为主体行驶这四种基本的流动。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background: white; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 0em; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appf3KZT3728192/image/ueditor/12994900_1541637247.cn/mmbiz_jpg/b4mklbpgc03hfxrrqfnmuinoanzhxmciaqygqawyawadavmakyd6tuba3sblwo5n0icztbjoq8s7ibwhpqh64tz1w/640" title=".jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background: white; line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">曹洪仁，北京八界旅游咨询有限公司创始人、CEO，曾服务国际知名壹级总承包建筑工程公司、国内最大旅游咨询集团巅峰智业和中科院地理所旅游中心。兼任国内数十家文旅智库专家、文旅投资公司</span><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-indent: 0em;">投资顾问、政企文旅评审专家等。对国内外文化旅游及文旅目的地创建有深入独到的研究，主持参与创建文旅项目60多项，每年差旅行程20万公里+深入文旅一线，发表上百篇有广泛影响力的行业研究文章。在振兴乡村、特色小镇、田园综合体、国家级旅游度假区、AAAAA景区创建、庄园经济等方面有多个实践。所创立见学中国、八界文旅平台在文旅行业享有美誉。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 3px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: white; line-height: 2em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appf3KZT3728192/image/ueditor/30787600_1541637247.cn/mmbiz_jpg/b4mklbpgc03hfxrrqfnmuinoanzhxmcialkuv00oxurgcqflc6qndorydnljt55urjsstz5zfognhicem94uhshq/640" title=".jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background: white; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 16px;">1、文旅行业智力服务者，规划设计公司项目负责人，愿意接受新知识，愿意接受未来挑战；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background: white; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 16px;">2、为转型而焦虑、为发展而苦恼的传统旅游企业负责人；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background: white; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 16px;">3、文旅企业高管和战略部门负责人；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background: white; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 16px;">4、地方政府文旅部门，乡村振兴一线实践人员；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background: white; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 16px;">5、投资金融机构的一线人员。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background: white; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appf3KZT3728192/image/ueditor/42530000_1541637247.cn/mmbiz_jpg/b4mkl